-- int_deduped_channels.sql
```sql
-- Deduplicated customer channels picking the most recent attribution
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        customer_id,
        channel,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY customer_id
            ORDER BY attributed_at DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_customer_channels') }}
)
SELECT
    customer_id,
    channel
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- fct_revenue_by_channel_city.sql
```sql
-- Final fact table calculating customer revenue by attribution channel and city
SELECT
    COALESCE(ch.channel, '(unknown)') AS channel,
    COALESCE(s.city, '(unknown)') AS city,
    SUM(t.amount) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(t.transaction_id) AS transaction_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT t.customer_id) AS unique_customers
FROM {{ ref('stg_transactions') }} t
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_channels') }} ch
    ON t.customer_id = ch.customer_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_stores') }} s
    ON t.store_id = s.store_id
GROUP BY
    COALESCE(ch.channel, '(unknown)'),
    COALESCE(s.city, '(unknown)')
